[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1709","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1709.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1127","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 Named Pipes Over RPC 资源耗尽拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 的远程过程调用（RPC）服务在处理命名管道（Named Pipes Over RPC）连接时存在资源管理缺陷，未能正确关闭无效的命名管道 RPC 连接。未经身份认证的远程攻击者可向目标系统发起一系列包含畸形数据的连接请求，由于系统无法及时释放这些失败连接所占用的资源，最终导致系统资源（如内存、句柄等）被持续耗尽，引发拒绝服务（DoS）。该漏洞影响运行 Windows NT 4.0 的服务器与工作站，攻击仅需网络可达目标主机的 RPC 端口，无需任何凭据即可远程触发，利用方式是通过反复建立并发送畸形数据连接使目标系统资源枯竭而停止响应。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1127"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:46.667","remediation":"立即安装微软发布的 Windows NT 4.0 安全补丁（SP4 及之后补丁包，对应修复\"Named Pipes Over RPC\"漏洞的更新），通过 Windows Update 或手动部署补丁程序。如无法立即打补丁，应在边界防火墙或路由器上过滤 135、139、445 等 RPC/NetBIOS 端口的入站连接，并仅允许受信任内网主机访问命名管道服务，以缓解远程资源耗尽攻击。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/Q195/7/33.asp","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/523.php","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1998/ms98-017","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/712a40967986b700313860b08048435be4fa9839/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1127.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1127","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1127.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24512263eb77d6af2cecd67bd2460f761fc94bea/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1127.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-fjjp-8g8w-55f2/GHSA-fjjp-8g8w-55f2.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cwe_details/cwe_details_700_800.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86274/info.html","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--104a9cd6-dbd0-4dfc-807e-78202b058454.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1127.json","https://github.com/fklement/acema_oran/blob/096561d274c61aab60b54a37c9ceb0c29a73e6fb/O-Cloud%20-%20Data%20Gathering.ipynb"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1709.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1708","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1708.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1094","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 缓冲区溢出远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Internet Explorer 4.01 及更早版本中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标用户发送包含特制长 URL 的链接，利用 \"mk:\" 协议触发缓冲区溢出，从而在用户浏览器中执行任意命令。该漏洞影响 Windows 平台上的 Internet Explorer 4.01 及更早版本，攻击者需诱导用户点击恶意链接，无需其他认证条件，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1094"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:42.553","remediation":"立即安装 Microsoft 安全公告中提供的修补程序（KB 文章 Q176697），该补丁修复了 Internet Explorer 中 mk: 协议处理程序的长 URL 缓冲区溢出问题。鉴于 IE 4.01 及更早版本已停止技术支持，建议升级到受支持的 Microsoft Edge 浏览器；如无法升级，可通过注册表禁用 mk: 协议处理器，在 HKEY_CLASSES_ROOT\\mk\\shell\\open\\command 中将默认值清空作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=88480839506155&w=2","http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/q176/6/97.asp","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/917","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/7481e97cf7b60a5b982d99d7dad1ea61174940fb/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1094.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1094","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1094.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/c1321b1a6b0cb3a4c18f791e2c8443742c0cb0b0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1094.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-wcrg-6ghq-6288/GHSA-wcrg-6ghq-6288.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88085/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1094.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000992.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1708.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1708.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1708.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1706","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1706.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1087","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 4 无点IP地址安全区域绕过漏洞","description":"Internet Explorer 4 在处理 URL 中的无点 IP 地址（32 位数字）时存在解析错误漏洞，将此类数字错误解析为主机名而非 IP 地址，导致浏览器对结果网页应用本地 Intranet 区域安全策略而非 Internet 区域策略。远程攻击者可通过构造包含无点 IP 地址的恶意 URL 诱导用户访问，绕过 IE 的 Internet 区域安全限制，在本地 Intranet 权限下执行未授权操作。该漏洞影响 Internet Explorer 4 版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1087"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:41.647","remediation":"升级至 Internet Explorer 5 或更高版本，该问题已在后续版本中修复。若无法升级，手动将 dotless IP 格式的 URL（如 http://1234567890/）加入受限制站点列表，并启用最高安全级别以阻止此类绕过行为。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/q168/6/17.asp","http://www.microsoft.com/Windows/Ie/security/dotless.asp","http://www.osvdb.org/7828","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1998/ms98-016","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2209","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/7481e97cf7b60a5b982d99d7dad1ea61174940fb/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1087.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1087","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1087.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/c1321b1a6b0cb3a4c18f791e2c8443742c0cb0b0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1087.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-9rv3-rxw8-xr7c/GHSA-9rv3-rxw8-xr7c.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1087.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--99ba35f8-d4eb-4aae-be83-0d60e01586a1.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88079/info.html","https://github.com/williamjsmail/piranha/blob/e60f12e6edcde8585ee473f701c2421f6efe72d9/CVE2CAPEC/database/CVE-1999.jsonl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1706.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1687","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1687.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1055","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9123,\"outputTokens\":21,\"totalTokens\":10808}}","description":"Microsoft Excel 97 在执行工作表函数前不会向用户发出任何警告或确认提示。攻击者可在恶意构造的 Excel 文档中利用内置的 CALL 工作表函数加载并执行一个恶意的 DLL 动态链接库，从而在受害者系统上执行任意命令。该漏洞影响 Microsoft Excel 97 版本，攻击条件为诱导用户打开特制的 Excel 文件，属于典型的恶意文档投递型代码执行漏洞，用户一旦打开文档即可能在无感知的情况下被远程控制。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1055"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:36.767","remediation":"将 Microsoft Excel 升级到 Office 2000 SR-1 或安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-022 提供的补丁，该补丁已禁止 CALL 函数加载外部 DLL。如暂时无法升级，可在组策略中禁用 Excel 加载宏与调用外部函数，并限制用户打开来自不可信来源的 Excel 文档，以避免通过恶意工作簿执行恶意 DLL。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/179","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1998/ms98-018","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1737","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dde4d96d7c1eff197b9a15817af615500736afa7/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1055.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1055","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1055.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2d0833866f347223eab80ef68cc3e2461a4e724d/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1055.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-cx75-p9pm-2q97/GHSA-cx75-p9pm-2q97.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cwe_details/cwe_details_600_700.json","https://github.com/Team-Atlanta/aixcc-asc-atlantis/blob/785c446f980e12155935db586aa30c3b54adcc86/crs/src/crs-patch/smith/smith/lib/cwe/raw/CWE-356.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1055.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/Christopher0129/security-knowledge-base/blob/ecec748afe5bbe2fcd2fd04b00fb46bc827b2c5d/system-vulnerabilities/windows.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1687.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1207","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1207.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1590","title":"Muhammad A. Muquit wwwcount 目录遍历漏洞","description":"wwwcount（Count.cgi）2.3 版本存在目录遍历漏洞，其 CGI 程序在处理 image 参数时未对用户输入进行充分过滤与校验，攻击者可构造包含\"..\"路径回溯序列的恶意请求读取服务器上任意位置的 GIF 文件。该漏洞影响部署了 Muhammad A. Muquit 所编写 wwwcount 2.3 组件的 Web 服务器，远程未授权攻击者仅需向 Count.cgi 发送特制 URL 即可利用，无需身份认证或特殊权限，属于信息泄露类安全问题。","severity":"LOW","score":3.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1590"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:47.250","remediation":"建议将 wwwcount (Count.cgi) 升级至 2.3 以外的版本（该漏洞仅影响 2.3 版本，更早版本不受此问题影响），或直接替换为其他 maintained 的网站访问计数器程序。如短期内无法升级，可在 Web 服务器层面对 Count.cgi 的 image 参数进行输入过滤，去除 \"..\" 及绝对路径字符，或在 CGI 执行目录中限制 Count.cgi 的读取权限，阻止其访问文档根目录以外的文件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://seclists.org/bugtraq/1997/Oct/0058.html","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5a67adc3536b9edff12a57c2de9cd5aa5d12653d/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1590.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1590","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-1590.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/9e7373a0dc9acbc4f26666870ca31dd641df9b83/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1590.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/2e86ccb45bad26f6ff984e676f6d08b925d0e6ee/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-jfr4-hpqv-2pq4/GHSA-jfr4-hpqv-2pq4.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87918/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/178b809924783e13787d17bb1b1fd55ad3b8639b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1590.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001065.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1207.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1207.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1207.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1205","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1205.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1589","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9110,\"outputTokens\":18,\"totalTokens\":10792}}","description":"IBM AIX 3.2 操作系统中的 crontab 组件存在一处未明确说明的安全漏洞。由于该漏洞的具体成因与攻击向量在公开资料中未予披露，仅确认其属于本地权限提升类缺陷。已登录目标系统的本地用户可利用该漏洞，通过尚未公开的攻击方式将自身权限提升至 root 超级用户，从而完全控制受影响的 AIX 3.2 主机，读取、篡改或破坏系统关键数据并执行任意高权限操作。该漏洞影响范围为运行 IBM AIX 3.2 版本的系统，攻击前提条件是攻击者需先获得目标主机的本地普通用户访问权限，CVSS 评分为 7.2，危害等级为高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1589"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:47.120","remediation":"建议将 IBM AIX 升级至受支持的 5.3/6.1/7.x 版本（AIX 3.2 已停止维护，无官方补丁）；在无法立即升级时，临时将 crontab 二进制文件权限收紧为 755 属主 root，移除其他用户的 setuid 位（chmod 755 /usr/bin/crontab），并限制仅授权用户访问 /var/spool/cron/crontabs 目录以缓解本地提权风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.cert.org/advisories/CA-1992-10.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/357","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5a67adc3536b9edff12a57c2de9cd5aa5d12653d/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1589.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1589","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-1589.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/9e7373a0dc9acbc4f26666870ca31dd641df9b83/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1589.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/2e86ccb45bad26f6ff984e676f6d08b925d0e6ee/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-j4jq-crhw-x9w5/GHSA-j4jq-crhw-x9w5.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1589.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--a4264527-93ec-4449-abae-a0eb85812356.json","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idgainpre","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_gainpre.txt","https://github.com/xXRenzoElProXx/secdash/blob/f8567f96d1554fc10942b9c14b4840ffde38fe05/shared_data/ag9.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1205.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1201","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1201.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1585","title":"Sun Solaris rcS/mountall 权限提升漏洞","description":"Sun Solaris 2.x 系统在启动过程中，rcS 和 mountall 程序在 fsck 文件系统检查失败时会自动在系统控制台启动一个特权 shell（root 权限），攻击者通过物理接触目标系统控制台即可获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 Solaris 2.4 之前版本，利用条件要求攻击者具有物理访问权限，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1585"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:46.540","remediation":"建议升级到已修复的 Solaris 2.5 或更高版本（安装 Sun 官方补丁 103594 系列），并在无法立即升级时于系统控制台物理加锁、限制物理访问，同时在启动脚本中对 fsck 失败做显式处理并禁用自动进入特权 shell 的行为。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/search/document.do?assetkey=1-22-00124-1","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/64fd197c5b8f3e4f9493cb07798bdca54583505c/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1585.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1585","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-1585.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f71c1815da5fc1872d1d999eebe8b28a9e3854c7/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1585.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/2e86ccb45bad26f6ff984e676f6d08b925d0e6ee/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-fp24-hwrr-3jqm/GHSA-fp24-hwrr-3jqm.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87917/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/178b809924783e13787d17bb1b1fd55ad3b8639b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1585.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001060.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1201.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1201.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1131","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1131.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1488","title":"IBM Scalable POWERparallel SP 2.0 sdrd 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"IBM SP2 系统数据存储库 (SDR) 中的 sdrd 守护进程存在未授权文件读取漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份验证即可通过 sdrd 守护进程读取系统任意文件。该漏洞影响 IBM Scalable POWERparallel (SP) 2.0 系统中的 SP2 System Data Repository (SDR) 组件，CVSS 评分 5.0（中等严重性）。攻击者可利用 sdrd 守护进程的权限验证缺陷，远程匿名读取系统敏感文件，导致敏感信息泄露。IBM 已发布相关补丁修复该漏洞，建议受影响用户及时升级修补。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1488"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:32.927","remediation":"建议升级至 IBM SP2 System Data Repository (SDR) 修补版本或升级至更新版本的 IBM POWERparallel 系统。若无法升级，请在防火墙层面封锁 sdrd 守护进程监听端口（默认 TCP 端口），或在不使用 SDR 服务时彻底禁用 sdrd 守护进程；同时配置网络访问控制列表 (ACL) 限制仅受信管理网段可访问 SDR 服务端口，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/i-079a.shtml","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7217.php","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/371","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19297","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/73dad9db65989a09e468a4f3a98f0eea36f0346c/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1488.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1488","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-1488.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/5297adfba5e91ee22e711c26c523b292d427c0d0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1488.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/90b464bbc2d1b64270a5771429f96b67fbe9e79b/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-pjw4-g8gx-f3vw/GHSA-pjw4-g8gx-f3vw.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1488.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001057.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--bf75d5a4-a29d-4870-8c70-82759ed4d7ed.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1131.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1128","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1128.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1481","title":"美国国家科学基金会 Squid Web Proxy 认证绕过漏洞","description":"Squid Web Proxy 2.2.STABLE5 及更早版本在使用外部认证程序时，未正确处理用户名/密码中的换行符，导致认证绕过漏洞。攻击者可在认证凭据中注入换行符，绕过访问控制列表（ACL）检查，从而绕过身份验证获得未授权的代理访问权限。该漏洞影响 Squid 1.0、1.1、2.1 及 2.2.STABLE5 及更早版本，攻击前提是 Squid 配置了外部认证程序（如 NCSA、LDAP 等）。攻击者只需在认证时提交包含换行符的用户名/密码组合即可绕过访问控制，CVSS 评分 5.0，属中等严重性漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1481"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:32.043","remediation":"建议升级 Squid 至 2.2.STABLE6 或更高版本（官方已修复换行符注入漏洞），或升级至 3.x/4.x 稳定分支。若暂时无法升级，请禁用 external_acl_type 等外部认证模块，改用内置 basic/ntlm/digest 认证，并在前置代理/防火墙层面过滤用户名密码中的换行符（%0A/%0D）作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/33295","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/741","http://www.squid-cache.org/Versions/v2/2.2/bugs/","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3433","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19567","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/73dad9db65989a09e468a4f3a98f0eea36f0346c/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1481.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1481","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-1481.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/57cb981038a97031bd95a35a9b10bbed18ca4725/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1481.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/90b464bbc2d1b64270a5771429f96b67fbe9e79b/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-fx2h-93c2-339q/GHSA-fx2h-93c2-339q.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_2.list.dict","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--fae97c09-d960-49db-879c-a19db82392f0.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1481.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1128.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1128.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1128.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1125","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1125.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1476","title":"Intel Pentium 处理器拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Intel Pentium 处理器（MMX 和 Overdrive 型号）存在指令处理缺陷，本地攻击者可通过执行带有锁定前缀的非法 CMPXCHG8B 指令，导致处理器进入未定义状态，进而引发基于 Intel 的操作系统（如 Windows NT 和 Windows 95）挂起或崩溃，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞利用条件简单，攻击者仅需具备本地用户权限即可触发，无需特殊系统权限。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1476"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:31.403","remediation":"Windows NT 4.0 用户应安装 Service Pack 4 或更高版本（含 SP4 及后续更新），该补丁通过修改 HAL 层拦截无效指令传递至处理器。Windows NT 3.51 用户需安装微软提供的 pent-fix 热修复补丁，替换 Hal.dll 和 Ntkrnlmp.exe 等内核文件。Windows 95 无官方修复，建议升级至 Windows 98 或更高版本。如无法升级，可在应用层对 CMPXCHG8B 指令进行输入校验，阻止恶意程序执行该非法操作码。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/q163/8/52.asp","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/704"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1125.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1123","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1123.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1473","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 页面重定向认证信息泄露漏洞","description":"Internet Explorer 3.02 及 4.0 版本存在页面重定向认证信息泄露漏洞。当用户访问一个恶意网站时，该网站可将浏览器重定向至攻击者控制的第三方站点，而浏览器会自动将用户在原站点的认证信息（如 NTLM 凭据）发送给重定向目标站点，导致敏感认证信息泄露。攻击者无需特殊权限，仅需诱导用户访问恶意链接即可利用该漏洞。此漏洞影响范围广泛，可导致用户账户凭据被窃取。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1473"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:31.017","remediation":"立即升级 Internet Explorer 至 5.0 及以上版本，该漏洞已在 IE 5.0 中修复。对于无法升级的旧系统，可配置 IE 安全区域为「高」级别并禁用跨域访问自动传递凭据的选项。同时建议在代理服务器或网关层面过滤 HTTP Referer 头中的认证信息，防止重定向场景下凭据泄露。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/q176/6/97.asp","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7426.php","http://www.osvdb.org/7818","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/58a0ea900decdd7e971b95fcaa99234de5a5df5e/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1473.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1473","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1473.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/dabf5b9888e8885cf125c5729901a7ad84d00092/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1473.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/18de81c56daca1c9e33223f0b95bdb8312a1ca75/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-rc82-f234-qr88/GHSA-rc82-f234-qr88.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1473.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001053.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--87310f6c-e3e3-44bc-9d56-f665a8c48b4b.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87907/info.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1123.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1119","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1119.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1465","title":"Cisco IOS 分布式快速交换访问控制列表安全绕过漏洞","description":"Cisco IOS 11.1 至 11.3 版本中启用了分布式快速交换（DFS）功能的路由器存在访问控制列表绕过漏洞。当路由器将流量从启用了 DFS 的入站接口交换到具有逻辑子接口的出站接口时，远程攻击者可利用此缺陷绕过 ACL 访问控制列表的过滤规则，导致未授权网络流量进入受保护网络段。该漏洞影响 Cisco IOS 11.1-11.3 版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。Cisco 已发布安全公告并提供修复建议。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1465"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:29.897","remediation":"升级 Cisco IOS 至 11.3(6) 或更新版本以修复该漏洞。临时缓解措施：在接口配置模式下使用 `no ip route-cache distributed` 命令禁用分布式快速交换（DFS），或避免在启用了 DFS 的入站接口与逻辑子接口出站接口之间路由流量。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/j-016.shtml","http://www.cisco.com/warp/public/770/iosdfsacl-pub.shtml","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1401"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1119.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1117","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1117.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1462","title":"Big Brother bb-hist.sh CGI History 模块远程文件泄露漏洞","description":"Big Brother 1.09b 及 1.09c 版本的 CGI History 模块（bb-hist.sh）存在远程文件泄露漏洞。攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向该脚本发送特制请求，读取目标服务器上的任意文件内容，导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响 Big Brother 1.09b 和 1.09c 版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。目前厂商已发布更新修复此漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1462"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:29.523","remediation":"立即将 Big Brother 升级至 1.09d 或更高版本，该版本已修复 bb-hist.sh CGI 脚本中未正确限制文件读取路径的问题。如无法升级，可删除或禁用 CGI 目录下的 bb-hist.sh 脚本，并在 Web 服务器（如 Apache）配置中对 /cgi-bin/ 目录添加访问控制，仅允许授权 IP 访问。同时确保 CGI 脚本以低权限用户运行，限制其可读取的文件范围。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://bb4.com/README.CHANGES","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/13440","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/142","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3755","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e6863af1ae3bb1cd8c56c1f1aac61d836661ac74/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1462.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1462","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1462.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/1d279cde1e5f7d9e150ca373126c9b35476ad3f5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1462.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/bb-hist.nasl","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/18de81c56daca1c9e33223f0b95bdb8312a1ca75/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-fwqm-q5x9-cvjv/GHSA-fwqm-q5x9-cvjv.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/142/info.html","https://github.com/magicsword-io/Magic-SigExplorer/blob/2c28b91b003429a144a687199ee99ebd26f1a343/Magic-SigExplorer/docs/cve_report.md","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--0be18609-ef23-4332-9f03-c94852851693.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1117.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1114","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1114.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1456","title":"thttpd HTTP服务器 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"thttpd HTTP 服务器 2.03 及更早版本存在路径遍历漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标服务器发送包含多个连续斜杠（/）的 GET 请求，绕过路径限制读取服务器上的任意文件。该漏洞源于对 URL 路径中斜杠字符的处理缺陷，攻击者无需身份认证即可利用，可能导致敏感信息泄露。受影响版本包括 thttpd 2.03 及之前所有版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1456"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:28.777","remediation":"升级 thttpd 至 2.04 或更高版本（2.04 版本修复了文件名解析中的路径遍历漏洞）。如无法升级，可在 Web 服务器前端（如反向代理或 WAF）配置规则，拦截包含多个连续斜杠（如 //）的 GET 请求路径作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.acme.com/software/thttpd/thttpd.html#releasenotes","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/10368","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1809"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1114.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1113","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1113.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1455","title":"Microsoft Windows NT RSH 访问控制漏洞","description":"Windows NT 3.5 至 4.0 版本中的 RSH 服务 (RSHSVC) 存在访问控制漏洞。当用户从已授权主机发起连接时，该服务未能正确解析 .Rhosts 文件中的访问控制规则，导致来自同一授权主机的未授权用户也可绕过身份验证访问 RSH 服务。远程攻击者可利用此漏洞在目标系统上以 SYSTEM 权限执行任意命令，影响 Windows NT 3.5/4.0 等版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1455"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:28.633","remediation":"建议立即禁用 Windows NT 系统中的 RSH 服务 (RSHSVC)，该服务已过时且存在严重访问控制缺陷。打开服务管理器，找到 \"RSHSVC\" 或 \"Remote Shell Service\"，将启动类型改为\"禁用\"并停止服务。如业务必须使用远程 shell，应迁移至 SSH 服务（如安装 OpenSSH for Windows），并配置防火墙规则阻止外部对 TCP 端口 514 的访问作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/q158/3/20.asp","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/7422"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1113.toml"}]